{"tid":17793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[痴撚線]英國新鈔含動物脂肪 素食者7萬人聯署要求回收","createTime":"2016-12-02T03:21:28.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T03:35:18.000Z","uid":22680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e7866c8cab7f4ea839ce356faf90752ed6a27680","tid":17793,"uid":22680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:21:28.000Z","msg":"英國最近發行新的5英鎊塑膠鈔票，原來製造成份含有動物脂肪，引起純素主義者不滿，在網上發起聯署，要求英倫銀行回收，至周二已獲得逾7萬人簽名支持。<br />\n新的5英鎊面額塑膠鈔票是在9月發行，央行稱讚新鈔可防水，同時新增防偽特徵。不過有純素主義者表示，新鈔的聚合物顆粒中，含有來自動物脂肪的牛脂（Tallow）。<br />\n發起聯署的47歲純素主義者道格（Doug Maw），他強調在鈔票內使用動物脂肪「十分不尊重」，「數百萬純素主義者、素食者、印度教徒、錫克教徒、耆那教徒及其他英國人士無法接受」，他強調民眾對鈔票「無得揀」，「我們沒法選擇金錢，被迫要使用它，它們經自動櫃員機、或商店交到我們手中」。<br />\n英國央行承認新鈔含有牛脂，又指牛脂廣泛應用於製造肥皂、蠟燭，但對聯署未有作評論。<br />\n　<br />\n網民對聯署反應兩極，「身為素食者，我覺得這真是太瘋狂了，這是鈔票又不是食物」，「很多人都搞錯重點，這是關乎動物探討&hellip;&hellip;並非純素主義者無理取鬧，這是關於不想日常生活中，甚麼東西都要靠動物。」<br />\n但有人認為「為甚麼英國人要因為少數不食人間煙火的人，讓問題變得更複雜，也不想想我們就教育人們吃肉」，「對，不用動物脂肪的鈔票很純淨，大概只有那些個人衛生極佳的人才能碰」。<br />\n法新社/中央社  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20161201/55984614\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20161201%2F55984614&d=WPWOQTheSiAT%2FB2p9vAnAGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=63a708ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20161201%2F55984614&h=7ffa6a6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20161201/55984614</a>"},{"pid":"0d0e02ee397a56e50996923f4e9b4e1e1a317efb","tid":17793,"uid":10503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:28:17.000Z","msg":"石油都係動物屍體<br />\n唔好用塑膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"834850cfb7bc335361d8e7c333d382a129b0d7a4","tid":17793,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:30:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>石油都係動物屍體<br />\n唔好用塑膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 秒左d素食撚左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d22588f86feec24e1cda94263b3e0ebddf5fbe","tid":17793,"uid":4934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:31:37.000Z","msg":"Vegans真係好多都冇乜腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bb597ef0a73382e475a86fd47e1e044acff8485","tid":17793,"uid":8207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:31:52.000Z","msg":"叫你食咩依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"151036d07c64575859dd606b451a3af5c6f221bc","tid":17793,"uid":28758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:32:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫你食咩依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能人地鍾意奶錢呢"},{"pid":"4baee3fe158ec90fc5d0c9ee7d070e6f130b264c","tid":17793,"uid":22680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:33:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫你食咩依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩都要管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ced8e18fb0741f311c423c67c86ac7dbd3082c19","tid":17793,"uid":6038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:34:36.000Z","msg":"班素食怪又道德塔利班上身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9adbe8c01ecc8d04eb32a0feb2247845500c999b","tid":17793,"uid":10025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"